{"tid":284801,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【拳擊 vs MMA】Mayweather落實26/8鬥McGregor　出場費每人獲7.8億","createTime":"2017-06-15T08:44:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-15T09:17:07.000Z","uid":55851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a05503f2bce2fedf920a72453d796f8493c893d6","tid":284801,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T08:44:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://cdn.mmaweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/Mayweather-vs-McGregor-Fight-Poster-CM-Mock.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.mmaweekly.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F05%2FMayweather-vs-McGregor-Fight-Poster-CM-Mock.jpg&h=a749a604&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國拳擊世界冠軍梅韋特（Floyd Mayweather）於今晨的個人社交網站上載片段，宣布將會8月26日於拉斯維加斯決戰愛爾蘭拳手麥佳格（Conor McGregor）。梅韋特於2015年退休，兩年後宣布復出，相信是因為這場被喻為「金錢對決」（Money Fight）太誘人，估計都雙方可各獲1億美元（約7.8億港元）出場費。<br />\n<br />\n「落實了。」40歲的梅韋特於個人社交網站輕輕一說，宣布討論近一年的夢幻決鬥終於上演。這名不敗拳王職業生涯49戰全勝，於退休23個月後復出，與於終極格鬥擁有兩條拳王腰帶的麥佳格決戰。論年齡只得28歲的麥佳格明顯體能上佔優，只是今次雙方是帶上10盎司手套打12回合的154磅拳賽，未打過職業拳擊比賽的麥佳格經驗上較輸蝕，不過在1億美元出場費下，相信兩者都會搏到盡。<br />\n<br />\n不過麥佳格明顯信心十足，他更在於個人社交網站打上「決戰將來臨」，似乎毋懼迎戰史上其中一位最佳拳手。終極格鬥會長禮特便說：「我們籌備這場決鬥花了很多時間。麥佳格會一直追趕梅韋特，甚至嘗試將他擊倒。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/344891/xlarge/ff5965721d532e6db6ae34e7ae15a9ac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F344891%2Fxlarge%2Fff5965721d532e6db6ae34e7ae15a9ac.jpg&h=f4f9d56e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梅韋特第二度復出，今次他將會挑戰職業生涯第50勝。（Getty Images）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/280148/xlarge/771bf2980e8283a9efe807c3fa705d1d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F280148%2Fxlarge%2F771bf2980e8283a9efe807c3fa705d1d.jpg&h=e7ad8202&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n麥佳格在去年11月成為UFC賽事史上第一個同時擁有兩條拳王腰帶的拳手，其職業生涯獲21勝3負。（Getty Images）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2/98102/-%E6%8B%B3%E6%93%8A-%E6%A2%85%E9%9F%8B%E7%89%B9%E8%90%BD%E5%AF%A68-26%E9%AC%A5%E9%BA%A5%E4%BD%B3%E6%A0%BC-%E9%87%91%E9%8C%A2%E5%B0%8D%E6%B1%BA%E5%87%BA%E5%A0%B4%E8%B2%BB%E6%AF%8F%E4%BA%BA%E7%8D%B27-8%E5%84%84\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E9%25AB%2594%25E8%2582%25B2%2F98102%2F-%25E6%258B%25B3%25E6%2593%258A-%25E6%25A2%2585%25E9%259F%258B%25E7%2589%25B9%25E8%2590%25BD%25E5%25AF%25A68-26%25E9%25AC%25A5%25E9%25BA%25A5%25E4%25BD%25B3%25E6%25A0%25BC-%25E9%2587%2591%25E9%258C%25A2%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%25B1%25BA%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E8%25B2%25BB%25E6%25AF%258F%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%258D%25B27-8%25E5%2584%2584&d=XPfWdIJ1qqwkHC814Ko3JQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=e1e9544e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2/98102/-%E6%8B%B3%E6%93%8A-%E6%A2%85%E9%9F%8B%E7%89%B9%E8%90%BD%E5%AF%A68-26%E9%AC%A5%E9%BA%A5%E4%BD%B3%E6%A0%BC-%E9%87%91%E9%8C%A2%E5%B0%8D%E6%B1%BA%E5%87%BA%E5%A0%B4%E8%B2%BB%E6%AF%8F%E4%BA%BA%E7%8D%B27-8%E5%84%84</a>"},{"pid":"cedffd3ac0da3f7e5a706f4aaf890fb23dde5731","tid":284801,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T09:03:58.000Z","msg":"雖然睇落好似好白痴mma打 boxing <br />\n<br />\n但mc 條友d拳都好勁 而且後生 堅好睇<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最大利益都係搵錢姐"},{"pid":"e007ab46ad72ab34adf2f42671674b646ca7ee01","tid":284801,"uid":37735,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T09:06:55.000Z","msg":"拳擊車路士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b50b183414642b9a879cfbe656c225e54d4f034","tid":284801,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T09:17:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拳擊車路士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n對pacquiao唔車路士一定死緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}